      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:65:5",
      "text": [
        " إِنَّ عَلِيّاً ( عليه السلام ) كَرِهَ الصُّورَةَ فِي الْبُيُوتِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Al Musna, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said that Ali<sup>asws</sup> disliked the pictures in the houses’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from al-Muthanna’ who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, Alayhi al-Salam, has said that Ali, Alayhi al-Salam, disliked the existence of pictures in houses.’” "
        ]
      }
